choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for seven days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Day 1: Overnight oats with fruit and nuts (excluding almonds, pistachios, and cashews)
Day 2: Quinoa salad with grilled chicken and veggies
Day 3: Lentil soup with whole grain bread
Day 4: Grilled tofu stir-fry with brown rice and vegetables
Day 5: Chickpea curry with cauliflower rice
Day 6: Baked sweet potato with black beans and salsa
Day 7: Veggie burger on a whole grain bun with avocado and tomato
Enjoy your healthy meal plan!
